<h2><strong>Importance of diversity in education</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Diversity means the differences from one another person. This difference can be based on the country, religion, caste, language etc. The group of different kinds of people coming together is known as the <strong>unity in diversity</strong>.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><em><strong>Diversity in education means the classroom is filled with different types of students.</strong></em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Nowadays, diversity in education is on rising. Thousands of students go to study abroad. Many universities and colleges allow diverse people to study in a safe environment. The importance of diversity in education is more important to work globally. Diversity in education has many benefits which are most usable in today’s time.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

